    <h1>Why Discipline is Greater Than Motivation</h1>
    <p class="date">Published: 8 September 2025</p>

    <p>Motivation ek fuel hai, lekin wo temporary hota hai. Discipline ek engine hai jo har din aapko chalata hai — chahe mood ho ya na ho.</p>
    <p>Jo log sirf motivation ke bharose rehte hain wo short-term results paate hain. Lekin jo discipline banate hain wo consistency aur long-term success paate hain.</p>

